PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772381499
OL,3,CAmputation Support: Campaigners call
OL,4,Cfor more investment in life-changing
OL,5,Crehab
OL,7,FAfter losing his limbs to Strep A,
OL,8,FAlex has become a leading voice
OL,9,Fcampaigning for more investment in the
OL,10,Ftransition from hospital to normal
OL,11,Flife.
OL,13,FReflecting on his initial recovery,
OL,14,FAlex told ITV Meridian that while he
OL,15,Feventually regained his independence,
OL,16,Fthe process was more difficult than it
OL,17,Fneeded to be. He believes that a lack
OL,18,Fof early, specialized community
OL,19,Fsupport impacted his initial progress.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772381499
OL,3,CAmputation Support: Campaigners call
OL,4,Cfor more investment in life-changing
OL,5,Crehab
OL,7,F"I think in hindsight, if I had more
OL,8,Fsupport in the community, that would
OL,9,Fhave given me more confidence. I would
OL,10,Fhave got there in the end anyway, but
OL,11,Fit just would have hastened up the
OL,12,Fprocess to get me back to living as
OL,13,Findependently as I could.
OL,15,F"There needs to be greater
OL,16,Funderstanding around the cost of the
OL,17,Fequipment that is available; the
OL,18,FNational Health Service; and
OL,19,Fultimately how we get patients out of
OL,20,Frehab and into the community and make
OL,21,Fthat as seamless as possible."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
