CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772381499
OL,3,CAmputation Support: Campaigners call
OL,4,Cfor more investment in life-changing
OL,5,Crehab
OL,7,FStephen Cruz is the founder of the
OL,8,FAmputation Foundation. He is
OL,9,Fcampaigning for more investment in
OL,10,Frehabilitation during the first year
OL,11,Fof recovery.
OL,13,FHaving lost his own legs nearly 20
OL,14,Fyears ago in a road accident, Stephen
OL,15,Finsists more frequent appointments
OL,16,Fwould lead to much better long term
OL,17,Fhealth outcomes.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772381499
OL,3,CAmputation Support: Campaigners call
OL,4,Cfor more investment in life-changing
OL,5,Crehab
OL,7,F"You're going back to see the
OL,8,FProsthetist or the physio once a week
OL,9,Ffor a 20 minute session. You can't
OL,10,Fprogress. You only get I think about
OL,11,F12 sessions on the NHS of your physio
OL,12,Fto get you to that walking stage."
OL,14,FSome are able to access regular one on
OL,15,Fone support, where physiotherapists
OL,16,Finsist getting the start of the
OL,17,Fjourney right is key, but care is
OL,18,Fneeded throughout a patient's life.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772381499
OL,3,CAmputation Support: Campaigners call
OL,4,Cfor more investment in life-changing
OL,5,Crehab
OL,7,FCaroline Hardman, an amputation
OL,8,Frehabilitation specialist, said: "It's
OL,9,Fa huge thing having an amputation and
OL,10,Ftherefore having the team behind you
OL,11,Fto support you right from day one or
OL,12,Fif not before, is really, really
OL,13,Fcrucial for someone's recovery.
OL,15,F"It's a lifelong change to your life.
OL,16,FSo your first prosthetic leg won't be
OL,17,Fthe same as what you would have in
OL,18,Ffive years or ten years. Because
OL,19,Ftechnology might change.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772381499
OL,3,CAmputation Support: Campaigners call
OL,4,Cfor more investment in life-changing
OL,5,Crehab
OL,7,F"And so it's about empowering that
OL,8,Fperson to know what they can expect in
OL,9,Fthe future, what prosthetics are out
OL,10,Fthere, so they're in control. You
OL,11,Fknow, the possibilities are there."
OL,13,FNHS England has 35 prosthetics service
OL,14,Fcentres nationwide, which can see
OL,15,Faround 25,000 patients annually, with
OL,16,Fa range of providers including
OL,17,Fphysiotherapists and psychologists.
OL,19,FBut campaigners say levels of support
OL,20,Fcan still be a postcode lottery.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
